{"type":"message","id":"f8ad9eec","parentId":"06d6ad9c","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:19:31.879Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"function.exec:41","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"total 408\ndrwx------  11 wh1ko  staff    352 Mar 12 11:34 .\ndrwx------   9 wh1ko  staff    288 Mar 12 11:34 ..\n-rw-------   1 wh1ko  staff     46 Mar 12 11:34 __init__.py\ndrwx------   5 wh1ko  staff    160 Mar 12 11:34 __pycache__\n-rw-------   1 wh1ko  staff   8526 Mar 12 11:34 camofox_client.py\n-rw-------   1 wh1ko  staff  70616 Mar 12 11:34 fetch_china.py\n-rwx------   1 wh1ko  staff  79321 Mar 12 11:34 fetch_tweet.py\n-rw-------   1 wh1ko  staff  14114 Mar 12 11:34 sogou_wechat.py\n-rw-------   1 wh1ko  staff   3258 Mar 12 11:34 version_check.py\n-rw-------   1 wh1ko  staff   4276 Mar 12 11:34 x_discover.py\n-rw-------   1 wh1ko  staff   4214 Mar 12 11:34 x_mentions_nitter.py"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":19,"aggregated":"total 408\ndrwx------  11 wh1ko  staff    352 Mar 12 11:34 .\ndrwx------   9 wh1ko  staff    288 Mar 12 11:34 ..\n-rw-------   1 wh1ko  staff     46 Mar 12 11:34 __init__.py\ndrwx------   5 wh1ko  staff    160 Mar 12 11:34 __pycache__\n-rw-------   1 wh1ko  staff   8526 Mar 12 11:34 camofox_client.py\n-rw-------   1 wh1ko  staff  70616 Mar 12 11:34 fetch_china.py\n-rwx------   1 wh1ko  staff  79321 Mar 12 11:34 fetch_tweet.py\n-rw-------   1 wh1ko  staff  14114 Mar 12 11:34 sogou_wechat.py\n-rw-------   1 wh1ko  staff   3258 Mar 12 11:34 version_check.py\n-rw-------   1 wh1ko  staff   4276 Mar 12 11:34 x_discover.py\n-rw-------   1 wh1ko  staff   4214 Mar 12 11:34 x_mentions_nitter.py","cwd":"/Users/wh1ko/Documents/openclaw/agents/writer"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773641971876}}
{"type":"message","id":"abd5be47","parentId":"f8ad9eec","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:19:31.884Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"function.exec:42","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<div align=\"center\">\n\n# 🦞 x-tweet-fetcher\n\n**Fetch tweets, comments, timelines, and articles from X/Twitter — without login or API keys.**\n\n[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](LICENSE)\n[![OpenClaw Skill](https://img.shields.io/badge/OpenClaw-Skill-blue.svg)](https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw)\n[![Python 3.7+](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.7+-green.svg)](https://www.python.org)\n[![GitHub stars](https://img.shields.io/github/stars/ythx-101/x-tweet-fetcher?style=social)](https://github.com/ythx-101/x-tweet-fetcher)\n\n*Zero config · Agent-first JSON output · Cron-friendly exit codes · WeChat + X in one tool*\n\n[Quick Start](#-quick-start) · [Capabilities](#-capabilities) · [Cron Integration](#-cron-integration) · [How It Works](#-how-it-works)\n\n</div>\n\n---\n\n## 😤 Problem\n\n```\nYou: fetch that tweet for me\nAI:  I can't access X/Twitter. Please copy-paste the content manually.\n\nYou: ...seriously?\n```\n\nX has no free API. Scraping gets you blocked. Browser automation is fragile.\n\n**x-tweet-fetcher** solves this: one command → structured JSON, ready for your agent to consume. No API keys, no login, no cookies.\n\n## 📊 What You Get\n\n| Feature | Zero Deps | With Camofox | Output |\n|---------|:---------:|:------------:|--------|\n| Single tweet | ✅ | — | text, stats, media, quotes |\n| Reply comments | — | ✅ | threaded comment tree |\n| User timeline | — | ✅ | paginated tweet list (up to 200) |\n| X Articles (long-form) | — | ✅ | full article text |\n| X Lists | — | ✅ | paginated tweet list |\n| @mentions monitor | — | ✅ | incremental new mentions |\n| WeChat article search | ✅ | — | title, url, author, date |\n| Tweet discovery | ✅ | optional | keyword search results |\n| Google search | — | ✅ | zero API key alternative |\n| Chinese platforms | partial | ✅ | Weibo/Bilibili/CSDN/WeChat |\n| User profile analysis | — | ✅ + LLM | MBTI, Big Five, topic graph |\n\n> **For AI Agents**: All output is structured JSON. Import as Python modules for direct integration. Exit codes are cron-friendly (`0`=nothing new, `1`=new content)."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":14,"aggregated":"<div align=\"center\">\n\n# 🦞 x-tweet-fetcher\n\n**Fetch tweets, comments, timelines, and articles from X/Twitter — without login or API keys.**\n\n[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](LICENSE)\n[![OpenClaw Skill](https://img.shields.io/badge/OpenClaw-Skill-blue.svg)](https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw)\n[![Python 3.7+](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.7+-green.svg)](https://www.python.org)\n[![GitHub stars](https://img.shields.io/github/stars/ythx-101/x-tweet-fetcher?style=social)](https://github.com/ythx-101/x-tweet-fetcher)\n\n*Zero config · Agent-first JSON output · Cron-friendly exit codes · WeChat + X in one tool*\n\n[Quick Start](#-quick-start) · [Capabilities](#-capabilities) · [Cron Integration](#-cron-integration) · [How It Works](#-how-it-works)\n\n</div>\n\n---\n\n## 😤 Problem\n\n```\nYou: fetch that tweet for me\nAI:  I can't access X/Twitter. Please copy-paste the content manually.\n\nYou: ...seriously?\n```\n\nX has no free API. Scraping gets you blocked. Browser automation is fragile.\n\n**x-tweet-fetcher** solves this: one command → structured JSON, ready for your agent to consume. No API keys, no login, no cookies.\n\n## 📊 What You Get\n\n| Feature | Zero Deps | With Camofox | Output |\n|---------|:---------:|:------------:|--------|\n| Single tweet | ✅ | — | text, stats, media, quotes |\n| Reply comments | — | ✅ | threaded comment tree |\n| User timeline | — | ✅ | paginated tweet list (up to 200) |\n| X Articles (long-form) | — | ✅ | full article text |\n| X Lists | — | ✅ | paginated tweet list |\n| @mentions monitor | — | ✅ | incremental new mentions |\n| WeChat article search | ✅ | — | title, url, author, date |\n| Tweet discovery | ✅ | optional | keyword search results |\n| Google search | — | ✅ | zero API key alternative |\n| Chinese platforms | partial | ✅ | Weibo/Bilibili/CSDN/WeChat |\n| User profile analysis | — | ✅ + LLM | MBTI, Big Five, topic graph |\n\n> **For AI Agents**: All output is structured JSON. Import as Python modules for direct integration. Exit codes are cron-friendly (`0`=nothing new, `1`=new content).","cwd":"/Users/wh1ko/Documents/openclaw/agents/writer"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773641971879}}
{"type":"message","id":"15c5e82c","parentId":"abd5be47","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:19:50.136Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**🖤 收到，哥哥。本地工具链检查完成。**\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 本地可用联网搜索工具\n\n| 工具 | 命令 | 功能 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| **fetch-tweet** | `fetch-tweet --url` | 抓取 Twitter/X 推文 | ✅ 可用 |\n| **x-tweet-fetcher** | `python3 ~/.openclaw/tools/x-tweet-fetcher/scripts/` | 社交媒体抓取套件 | ✅ 可用 |\n| **chrome-cdp** | `~/.openclaw/skills/chrome-cdp/skills/chrome-cdp/scripts/cdp.mjs` | Chrome 浏览器自动化 | ✅ 可用 |\n| **web_search** | OpenClaw 内置 | Brave 搜索 API | ❌ **需 API Key** |\n| **web_fetch** | OpenClaw 内置 | 网页内容提取 | ✅ 可用 |\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 关键差异\n\n**公司侧有，本地缺失：**\n- `web_search` 需要 `BRAVE_API_KEY`（本地未配置）\n\n**本地有，功能完整：**\n- `fetch-tweet` ✅\n- `x-tweet-fetcher` 全套脚本 ✅\n- `chrome-cdp` ✅\n\n---\n\n## 📋 详细功能验证\n\n**x-tweet-fetcher 脚本清单：**\n```\nfetch_tweet.py      - Twitter/X 推文抓取\nfetch_china.py      - 微博/B站/CSDN/微信\nsogou_wechat.py     - 微信公众号搜索\nx_discover.py       - X 关键词搜索\nx_mentions_nitter.py - @mentions 监控\ncamofox_client.py   - Camofox 浏览器集成\n```\n\n---\n\n## 💡 建议\n\n**当前可用方案：**\n\n1. **Twitter/X 搜索** → `fetch-tweet` 或 `x-tweet-fetcher`\n2. **中文平台** → `fetch_china.py`（微博/B站/CSDN/微信）\n3. **通用网页** → `web_fetch`（需 URL）\n4. **Brave 搜索** → 需要配置 `BRAVE_API_KEY`\n\n**需要我：**\n- 测试某个具体搜索？\n- 配置 `BRAVE_API_KEY` 启用完整搜索？\n- 演示 `fetch-tweet` 或 `fetch_china.py` 使用？\n\n**🖤 等待指令。**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773641971885}}
