{"type":"message","id":"50897f35","parentId":"9f9aefae","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:34:00.587Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"function.process:48","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Agent Reach Installer\n========================================\nEnvironment: Local computer (auto-detected)\n\nChecking system dependencies...\n  ✅ gh CLI already installed\n  ✅ Node.js already installed\n  ✅ xreach CLI already installed\n  ✅ undici already installed (Node.js proxy support)\n  ✅ yt-dlp JS runtime already configured\nSetting up Weibo MCP server...\n  ✅ mcp-server-weibo installed (Panniantong fork)\n  ✅ Weibo MCP registered with mcporter\nSetting up Xiaoyuzhou podcast transcription...\n  ✅ Xiaoyuzhou transcription script already installed\n  -- ffmpeg not found. Install: apt install -y ffmpeg (or brew install ffmpeg)\n  -- Groq API key not set. Get free key at https://console.groq.com\n     Then run: agent-reach configure groq-key gsk_xxxxx\nSetting up WeChat article tools...\n  ✅ WeChat Python packages already installed\n  ✅ wechat-article-for-ai tool already installed\n\nSetting up mcporter (search + XiaoHongShu backend)...\n  ✅ mcporter already installed\n  ✅ Exa search already configured\n  -- XiaoHongShu MCP not detected (optional)\n     Install: docker run -d --name xiaohongshu-mcp -p 18060:18060 xpzouying/xiaohongshu-mcp\n     Then:    mcporter config add xiaohongshu http://localhost:18060/mcp\n     Repo:    https://github.com/xpzouying/xiaohongshu-mcp\n\nTrying to import cookies from browser...\n  -- No cookies found (normal if you haven't logged into these sites)\n\nTesting channels...\n\nAgent Reach 状态\n========================================\n\n✅ 装好即用：\n  ✅ GitHub 仓库和代码 — 完整可用（读取、搜索、Fork、Issue、PR 等）\n  ✅ YouTube 视频和字幕 — 可提取视频信息和字幕\n  ✅ V2EX 节点、主题与回复 — 公开 API 可用（热门主题、节点浏览、主题详情、用户信息）\n  ✅ RSS/Atom 订阅源 — 可读取 RSS/Atom 源\n  ✅ 全网语义搜索 — 全网语义搜索可用（免费，无需 API Key）\n  ✅ 任意网页 — 通过 Jina Reader 读取任意网页（curl https://r.jina.ai/URL）\n\n搜索（mcporter 即可解锁）：\n  ✅ Twitter/X 推文 — 完整可用（读取、搜索推文，含长文/X Article）\n  -- Reddit 帖子和评论 — 无代理。服务器 IP 可能被 Reddit 封锁。配置代理：\n  agent-reach configure proxy http://user:pass@ip:port\n  ✅ B站视频和字幕 — 可提取视频信息和字幕（本地环境）。服务器可能需要代理\n  ✅ 微博动态与热搜 — 完整可用（热搜、搜索、用户动态、评论）\n  -- 小宇宙播客转文字 — 需要 ffmpeg（音频转码和切片）。安装：\n  Ubuntu/Debian: apt install -y ffmpeg\n  macOS: brew install ffmpeg\n\n配置后可用：\n  -- 小红书笔记 — mcporter 已装但小红书 MCP 未配置。运行：\n  docker run -d --name xiaohongshu-mcp -p 18060:18060 xpzouying/xiaohongshu-mcp\n  mcporter config add xiaohongshu http://localhost:18060/mcp\n  -- 抖音短视频 — mcporter 已装但抖音 MCP 未配置。运行：\n  pip install douyin-mcp-server\n  # 启动服务后：\n  mcporter config add douyin http://localhost:18070/mcp\n  -- LinkedIn 职业社交 — mcporter 已装但 LinkedIn MCP 未配置。运行：\n  pip install linkedin-scraper-mcp\n  mcporter config add linkedin http://localhost:3000/mcp\n  ✅ 微信公众号文章 — 完整可用（搜索 + 阅读公众号文章）\n\n状态：10/15 个渠道可用\n运行 `agent-reach setup` 解锁更多渠道\n\nSkill installed for OpenClaw: /Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/agent-reach\nSkill installed for Agent: /Users/wh1ko/.agents/skills/agent-reach\n✅ Installation complete! 10/15 channels active.\n\nSome channels are not active yet. If you're an AI Agent, try to fix them yourself — then run `agent-reach doctor` again.\n\n如果 Agent Reach 帮到了你，给个 Star 让更多人发现它吧：\n   https://github.com/Panniantong/Agent-Reach\n   只需一秒，对独立开发者意义很大。谢谢！\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"glow-seaslug","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"\nAgent Reach Installer\n========================================\nEnvironment: Local computer (auto-detected)\n\nChecking system dependencies...\n  ✅ gh CLI already installed\n  ✅ Node.js already installed\n  ✅ xreach CLI already installed\n  ✅ undici already installed (Node.js proxy support)\n  ✅ yt-dlp JS runtime already configured\nSetting up Weibo MCP server...\n  ✅ mcp-server-weibo installed (Panniantong fork)\n  ✅ Weibo MCP registered with mcporter\nSetting up Xiaoyuzhou podcast transcription...\n  ✅ Xiaoyuzhou transcription script already installed\n  -- ffmpeg not found. Install: apt install -y ffmpeg (or brew install ffmpeg)\n  -- Groq API key not set. Get free key at https://console.groq.com\n     Then run: agent-reach configure groq-key gsk_xxxxx\nSetting up WeChat article tools...\n  ✅ WeChat Python packages already installed\n  ✅ wechat-article-for-ai tool already installed\n\nSetting up mcporter (search + XiaoHongShu backend)...\n  ✅ mcporter already installed\n  ✅ Exa search already configured\n  -- XiaoHongShu MCP not detected (optional)\n     Install: docker run -d --name xiaohongshu-mcp -p 18060:18060 xpzouying/xiaohongshu-mcp\n     Then:    mcporter config add xiaohongshu http://localhost:18060/mcp\n     Repo:    https://github.com/xpzouying/xiaohongshu-mcp\n\nTrying to import cookies from browser...\n  -- No cookies found (normal if you haven't logged into these sites)\n\nTesting channels...\n\nAgent Reach 状态\n========================================\n\n✅ 装好即用：\n  ✅ GitHub 仓库和代码 — 完整可用（读取、搜索、Fork、Issue、PR 等）\n  ✅ YouTube 视频和字幕 — 可提取视频信息和字幕\n  ✅ V2EX 节点、主题与回复 — 公开 API 可用（热门主题、节点浏览、主题详情、用户信息）\n  ✅ RSS/Atom 订阅源 — 可读取 RSS/Atom 源\n  ✅ 全网语义搜索 — 全网语义搜索可用（免费，无需 API Key）\n  ✅ 任意网页 — 通过 Jina Reader 读取任意网页（curl https://r.jina.ai/URL）\n\n搜索（mcporter 即可解锁）：\n  ✅ Twitter/X 推文 — 完整可用（读取、搜索推文，含长文/X Article）\n  -- Reddit 帖子和评论 — 无代理。服务器 IP 可能被 Reddit 封锁。配置代理：\n  agent-reach configure proxy http://user:pass@ip:port\n  ✅ B站视频和字幕 — 可提取视频信息和字幕（本地环境）。服务器可能需要代理\n  ✅ 微博动态与热搜 — 完整可用（热搜、搜索、用户动态、评论）\n  -- 小宇宙播客转文字 — 需要 ffmpeg（音频转码和切片）。安装：\n  Ubuntu/Debian: apt install -y ffmpeg\n  macOS: brew install ffmpeg\n\n配置后可用：\n  -- 小红书笔记 — mcporter 已装但小红书 MCP 未配置。运行：\n  docker run -d --name xiaohongshu-mcp -p 18060:18060 xpzouying/xiaohongshu-mcp\n  mcporter config add xiaohongshu http://localhost:18060/mcp\n  -- 抖音短视频 — mcporter 已装但抖音 MCP 未配置。运行：\n  pip install douyin-mcp-server\n  # 启动服务后：\n  mcporter config add douyin http://localhost:18070/mcp\n  -- LinkedIn 职业社交 — mcporter 已装但 LinkedIn MCP 未配置。运行：\n  pip install linkedin-scraper-mcp\n  mcporter config add linkedin http://localhost:3000/mcp\n  ✅ 微信公众号文章 — 完整可用（搜索 + 阅读公众号文章）\n\n状态：10/15 个渠道可用\n运行 `agent-reach setup` 解锁更多渠道\n\nSkill installed for OpenClaw: /Users/wh1ko/.openclaw/skills/agent-reach\nSkill installed for Agent: /Users/wh1ko/.agents/skills/agent-reach\n✅ Installation complete! 10/15 channels active.\n\nSome channels are not active yet. If you're an AI Agent, try to fix them yourself — then run `agent-reach doctor` again.\n\n如果 Agent Reach 帮到了你，给个 Star 让更多人发现它吧：\n   https://github.com/Panniantong/Agent-Reach\n   只需一秒，对独立开发者意义很大。谢谢！\n","name":"source ~/.agent-reach-venv/bin/activate"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773642840582}}
{"type":"message","id":"2613b648","parentId":"50897f35","timestamp":"2026-03-16T06:34:19.099Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**✅ Agent-Reach 安装完成！**\n\n---\n\n## 📊 安装结果\n\n| 状态 | 数量 | 渠道 |\n|------|------|------|\n| ✅ 装好即用 | 7 | GitHub、YouTube、V2EX、RSS、全网搜索、任意网页、微信公众号 |\n| ✅ 搜索可用 | 3 | Twitter/X、B站、微博 |\n| ⚠️ 需配置 | 5 | Reddit(代理)、小宇宙(ffmpeg)、小红书(Docker)、抖音、LinkedIn |\n\n**总计：10/15 渠道已激活**\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 已安装组件\n\n| 组件 | 位置 |\n|------|------|\n| Python 虚拟环境 | `~/.agent-reach-venv/` |\n| Agent-Reach 配置 | `~/.agent-reach/` |\n| OpenClaw Skill | `~/.openclaw/skills/agent-reach/` |\n| Agent Skill | `~/.agents/skills/agent-reach/` |\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 立即可用的功能\n\n```bash\n# GitHub 搜索\ngh search repos \"LLM framework\"\n\n# YouTube 字幕提取\nyt-dlp --dump-json \"https://youtube.com/watch?v=xxx\"\n\n# 全网语义搜索（免费，无需 API Key）\nmcporter call 'exa.web_search_exa(query: \"AI Agent 框架对比\")'\n\n# 微博热搜\nmcporter call 'weibo.get_trendings(limit: 10)'\n\n# 任意网页阅读\ncurl -s \"https://r.jina.ai/https://example.com\"\n\n# Twitter/X 搜索（需配置 Cookie）\nxreach search \"关键词\" --json\n```\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 可选配置\n\n| 渠道 | 需要 | 命令 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Reddit | 代理 | `agent-reach configure proxy http://user:pass@ip:port` |\n| 小宇宙播客 | ffmpeg | `brew install ffmpeg` |\n| 小红书 | Docker | `docker run -d --name xiaohongshu-mcp -p 18060:18060 xpzouying/xiaohongshu-mcp` |\n| Twitter/X 搜索 | Cookie | `agent-reach configure twitter-cookies \"...\"` |\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 下一步\n\n**需要我：**\n1. **运行 `agent-reach doctor` 详细检查？**\n2. **配置某个特定渠道（如 Twitter Cookie）？**\n3. **测试某个功能？**\n4. **同步 GEP 进化日志？**\n\n**🖤 Agent-Reach 已就绪，等待指令。**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773642840589}}
