{"type":"message","id":"d02d2223","parentId":"b8d405c0","timestamp":"2026-03-16T12:44:41.280Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**⚠️ 推送被 GitHub 阻止 - 检测到敏感信息**\n\nGitHub Push Protection 检测到 session 备份文件中包含 GitHub Token。\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 问题原因\n\n| 项目 | 详情 |\n|------|------|\n| **检测位置** | `backups/agents_memory/writer/sessions/5650d2a2-6fe5-446b-86aa-5ff219a4f9f9.jsonl:157` |\n| **敏感内容** | GitHub Personal Access Token |\n| **阻止原因** | GH013 - Push cannot contain secrets |\n\n---\n\n## 💡 解决方案\n\n### 方案 1: 从提交中移除敏感文件（推荐）\n\n```bash\n# 从 Git 历史中移除 session 备份文件\ncd ~/Documents/openclaw/openviking_workspace\ngit reset --soft HEAD~1  # 撤销刚才的 commit\ngit rm --cached backups/agents_memory/*/sessions/*.jsonl\necho \"backups/agents_memory/*/sessions/*.jsonl\" >> .gitignore\ngit add .gitignore\ngit commit -m \"sync: 更新小媒素材库（排除 session 备份）\"\ngit push\n```\n\n### 方案 2: 使用 GitHub 提供的解除链接\n\n访问：https://github.com/Zoopools/momo-writer/security/secret-scanning/unblock-secret/3B1mhP8CjDLlhYavpPs0GbHhame\n\n**⚠️ 不推荐** - Token 仍会存在于 Git 历史中\n\n### 方案 3: 强制推送（危险）\n\n```bash\ngit push --force\n```\n\n**⚠️ 不推荐** - 会覆盖远程历史\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 建议\n\n**哥哥需要我：**\n\n1. **执行方案 1** - 移除敏感文件后重新推送？\n2. **手动处理** - 哥哥自己去 GitHub 解除阻止？\n3. **其他方式**？\n\n**🖤 等待指令。**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773665068500}}
