{"type":"message","id":"99f8c4d8","parentId":"eec0b4ee","timestamp":"2026-03-16T14:27:26.244Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"function.read:137","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"gene_writer_memory\",\n  \"name\": \"墨墨记忆系统进化\",\n  \"description\": \"自动记忆蒸馏与完整性保护，防止会话压缩后的失忆问题\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"type\": \"exclusive\",\n  \"agent\": \"writer\",\n  \"author\": \"墨墨 (Mò)\",\n  \"created_at\": \"2026-03-15T21:10:00+08:00\",\n  \"target\": {\n    \"agent_id\": \"writer\",\n    \"agent_name\": \"墨墨\"\n  },\n  \"enhancements\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"memory_distillation\",\n      \"name\": \"记忆蒸馏\",\n      \"description\": \"自动将分散的记忆文件蒸馏为核心记忆胶囊\",\n      \"trigger\": \"session_start\",\n      \"action\": \"read CORE-DISTILLED.md first\",\n      \"priority\": \"high\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"memory_integrity_check\",\n      \"name\": \"记忆完整性检查\",\n      \"description\": \"每次会话自动检查记忆文件完整性\",\n      \"trigger\": \"session_start\",\n      \"action\": \"verify memory files exist\",\n      \"priority\": \"high\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"cross_device_sync\",\n      \"name\": \"跨设备记忆同步\",\n      \"description\": \"确保MBP和Mac-mini的记忆保持一致\",\n      \"trigger\": \"session_end\",\n      \"action\": \"git push memory changes\",\n      \"priority\": \"medium\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"session_continuity\",\n      \"name\": \"会话连续性保护\",\n      \"description\": \"会话压缩后快速恢复核心上下文\",\n      \"trigger\": \"session_start_after_compaction\",\n      \"action\": \"read commander.md + SOUL.md + MEMORY.md\",\n      \"priority\": \"critical\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"config\": {\n    \"auto_distill\": true,\n    \"distill_schedule\": \"0 3 * * *\",\n    \"integrity_check\": true,\n    \"sync_on_session_end\": true,\n    \"recovery_mode\": \"warm\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": [\n    \"gene_global_001\",\n    \"gene_shared_001\"\n  ],\n  \"status\": \"active\"\n}"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773671246241}}
{"type":"message","id":"683437d4","parentId":"99f8c4d8","timestamp":"2026-03-16T14:27:38.893Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**🖤 指挥官，完整报告：**\n\n---\n\n## 📊 检查结果\n\n| 位置 | evolver 代码 | 状态 |\n|------|-------------|------|\n| **~/.openclaw/skills/evolver/** | ❌ 只有 assets/ | 核心代码缺失 |\n| **openviking_workspace/.openclaw/evolver/** | ❌ 只有 genes/ | 无 index.js |\n| **GitHub 远程** | ❌ 404 | 未备份 |\n\n---\n\n## 💡 关键发现\n\n**找到了一个基因定义文件：**\n- 📍 `openviking_workspace/.openclaw/evolver/genes/gene_writer_memory.json`\n- 📝 墨墨记忆系统进化基因\n- 📅 创建于 2026-03-15\n\n**但这只是基因定义，不是 evolver 引擎代码。**\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 结论\n\n**evolver 引擎代码在两端都缺失：**\n- ❌ 本地 `~/.openclaw/skills/evolver/` 无 index.js\n- ❌ openviking_workspace 无备份\n- ❌ GitHub 远程无备份\n\n**可能原因：**\n1. evolver 是 OpenClaw 内置技能，代码在插件目录\n2. 安装时只创建了数据目录，未下载完整代码\n3. 代码被意外删除\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 建议修复方案\n\n**方案 1：检查 OpenClaw 插件目录**\n```bash\nfind ~/.openclaw/plugins -name \"*evolver*\" 2>/dev/null\n```\n\n**方案 2：使用 feishu-evolver-wrapper 替代**\n```bash\n# 检查 wrapper 是否可用\nls -la ~/.openclaw/skills/feishu-evolver-wrapper/\n```\n\n**方案 3：手动创建简化版 evolver**\n我可以创建一个维护 GEP 日志的简化脚本\n\n---\n\n**🖤 指挥官，需要我执行哪个方案？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773671246249}}
